THE MEASUREMENT OF DEFERRED TAX ASSETS IS REDUCED BY A VALUATION ALLOWANCE IF, BASED UPON AVAILABLE EVIDENCE, IT IS MORE-LIKELY-THAN-NOT THAT SOME OR ALL OF THE DEFERRED TAX ASSETS WILL NOT BE REALIZED.

