$44

ON UNDISTRIBUTED EARNINGS NOT CONSIDERED INDEFINITELY REINVESTED IN OUR NON-U.S. SUBSIDIARIES. WE HAVE NOT PROVIDED FOR U.S. DEFERRED INCOME TAXES OR FOREIGN WITHHOLDING TAX ON THE REMAINDER OF UNDISTRIBUTED EARNINGS FROM OUR NON-U.S. SUBSIDIARIES OF APPROXIMATELY

$775

BECAUSE SUCH EARNINGS ARE CONSIDERED TO BE INDEFINITELY REINVESTED AND IT IS NOT PRACTICABLE TO ESTIMATE THE AMOUNT OF TAX THAT MAY BE PAYABLE UPON DISTRIBUTION.

